#: ../../language/error_codes/E4102.md:1
msgid "E4102"
msgstr ""

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4102.md:3
msgid "Outside of a loop."
msgstr "不在循环中。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4102.md:5
msgid ""
"This error occurs when using `break` or `continue` statements outside of a "
"loop construct. These control flow statements can only be used within loops."
msgstr "该错误发生在使用 `break` 或 `continue` 语句时，它们只能在循环中使用。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4102.md:8
msgid "`break` is used to exit a loop early"
msgstr "`break` 用于提前退出循环。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4102.md:9
msgid "`continue` is used to skip to the next iteration of a loop"
msgstr "`continue` 用于跳过循环的下一次迭代。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4102.md:11
msgid ""
"Using these statements outside of a loop context is invalid since there is "
"no loop to break from or continue to the next iteration."
msgstr "在没有循环可跳出或继续到下一次迭代的情况下，使用这些语句是无效的。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4102.md:14
msgid "Erroneous example"
msgstr "错误示例"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4102.md:16
msgid ""
"pub fn f(xs: Array[Int]) -> Int {\n"
"  for i in xs {\n"
"    ignore(i)\n"
"  } else {\n"
"    break 42\n"
"//  ^^^^^^^^ Error: 'break' outside of a loop\n"
"  }\n"
"}\n"
"\n"
"pub fn g(x: Int) -> Int {\n"
"  continue x\n"
"// ^^^^^^^^ Error: 'continue' outside of a loop\n"
"}\n"
"\n"
"fn main {\n"
"  let x = { break }\n"
"//          ^^^^^ Error: 'break' outside of a loop\n"
"  println(x)\n"
"}"
msgstr ""

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4102.md:20
msgid "Suggestion"
msgstr "建议"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4102.md:22
msgid ""
"To fix this error, ensure that `break` and `continue` are used within a loop"
" construct."
msgstr "要修复此错误，请确保 `break` 和 `continue` 在循环构造中使用。"

